  "events": [],
  "moments": [
    {
      "id": "mo_001",
      "text": "My morning coffee was terrible, and my laptop took forever to boot up. I had this big presentation to prep, and I'm just so not in the mood today.",
      "tone": "frustrated",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_002",
      "text": "I just want to travel, you know? Maybe go to Kerala again. I'm so over work stuff right now.",
      "tone": "sad",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_003",
      "text": "Everything I sketch looks... annoyed. I need to get back to Kerala, I think. Or just take a day off and draw my feelings.",
      "tone": "frustrated",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_004",
      "text": "I need to draw my vacation before I actually take it.",
      "tone": "hopeful",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_005",
      "text": "Monsoon mornings are the best, but I've been missing them this year.",
      "tone": "sad",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_006",
      "text": "My ideal sketching mood is calm. Like, no deadlines, no notifications, just me and the page. Sometimes I light a candle too—makes it feel like I'm in one of those indie coffee ads where everyone's just… chill.",
      "tone": "content",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_007",
      "text": "sometimes I think the best art isn't 'meaningful'—it's just *you*, right in the moment.",
      "tone": "hopeful",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_008",
      "text": "Sleek, but only if it doesn't end up looking cheap. I want it to feel premium, not plastic.",
      "tone": "content",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-29",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-29",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_009",
      "text": "Triangles. Sharp, but not too aggressive. Like, the calm kind of sharp.",
      "tone": "content",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-29",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-29",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_010",
      "text": "Something that doesn't scream, you know? Just sits there quietly.",
      "tone": "content",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-29",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-29",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_011",
      "text": "Spice is basically the unsung hero of everything. Can't just be plain rice. Gotta be *spicy* rice. Or at least *meh* rice with a side of drama.",
      "tone": "playful",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-29",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-29",
      "mentions": 1
    }
  ],
